0.1 Example of function whatever

As Adams, Gottwald, and Leach (1986) or someone else stated it is important to be insulted if you do not recognise an even number:

iseven(3)
## [1] "Of course not you silly fool!"

Also it is important to have a function which tells you if the number is even:

iseven(2)
## [1] "Indeed it is an even number!"

As you can clearly see:

Now in Figure 1 a plot (Addiscott 1977).

plot(1,1,col="white")
text(1,1,returnname("Pendelhubstichsge"))

Figure 1: funplot
